"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-04-know-muffin-man-people-going-wild-swimmers-snack-olympics-21359026\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"There have been countless standout moments from theParisOlympics so far - fromC\\u00e9line Dion's incredible performanceat the opening ceremony toTeam GBwinning gold medals in rowing and trampoline.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is also been one majorly unexpected highlight for some sports fans, and it's all thanks to Norwegian distanceswimmerHenrik Christiansen.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\", \"score\": 0.8253422142642314, \"rank\": 0.21151063112064356, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old might not take home the gold, but he certainly has won the people's hearts thanks to a series of hilarious TikToks about asnackat the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1584795485134e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Village haspreviously hit headlines for its food, as Andy Anson, the British Olympic Association's chief executive, branded the meals 'inadequate'.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Anson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Henrik claims there is one item that's definitely worth eating, and he's even rated it an 11/10.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, it's not a croissant or pain au chocolat that the sports star has fallen for - it's a double chocolate muffin, with large chocolate chips and a gooey chocolate filling.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Henrik has gone viral online after sharing videos of himself eating the muffins, which he says are 'insane' and 'the single greatest thing about the Olympic Village.'\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1584795485134e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the clips show him looking lovingly at the snack, with chocolate smeared all over his face.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In one video, a fellow athlete shares a look at the inside of Henrik's bedside table, and the drawer is just full of muffins.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Guys, I think I have a problem,' the swimmer jokes in the caption.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As such, he's become known as the official 'Muffin Man' of the Olympics and he does not seem to be particularly upset about the title - in fact, he's embraced it.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The single greatest thing about the Olympic Village so far\\ud83e\\udd24#fyp#muffins#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage  I HEREBY DECLARE MYSELF AS THE OLYMPIC MUFFIN MAN#fyp#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#muffins@Olympics @paris2024  Those watching his videos are desperate to know absolutely everything they can about the muffins, with some asking for a documentary to be made about them.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1584795485134e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others are just in full support of the relationship between the man and the muffins.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope whoever makes these muffins sponsors you bc never have I so badly wanted a muffin before in my life,' commented @verticalsea.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly @xstormzcx said: 'The only thing I want right now is to sit in the olympic village and share a tea and a Muffin with this guy while we gossip about the Olympics.'\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At Metro Food, we are here to bring you all the latest foodie news, delicious recipes, restaurant reviews, and cooking tips.\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AT_Metro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"At Metro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AT_Metro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AT_Metro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a loyal reader and a part of our vibrant community, we want to make sure you never miss our articles when searching for stories  Click the button below and tickMetro.co.ukto ensure you see stories from us first in Google Search.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2717, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add us as a Preferred Source  From the latest Walkers flavours to the secret McDonald's menu, Metro Food has it all  @t0tally_not_averie wrote: 'Petition to have him in the next Shrek movie as the muffin man.'\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walkers_Limited\", \"score\": 0.9999999995779945, \"rank\": 2.4628040609173323e-10, \"text\": \"Walkers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walkers_Limited\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walkers_Limited\"}, {\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1266725604427606e-30, \"text\": \"Shrek\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And @valkyriefox.jpr shared: 'No better love story than a man and his muffins.'\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others wanted to know how to make the muffins, and said they'd be spending some time trying to recreate them at home.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chefs have even been sharing their own recipes for 'dupes'.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Guess who is competing today?#OlympicMuffinMan#Paris2024#MuffinMan  I GET THE HYPE.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(but only the middle part)#parisolympicschocolatemuffin#parisolympicsgamesvillage#paris2024#parisolympics#parisolympicsdininghall  Everyone is talking about the Olympic Chocolate Muffin, especially @Henrik Christiansen who made it go viral on TikTok this week.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3531, \"end\": 3537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.513997469723354e-54, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's my copycat recipe: a warm, decadent double chocolate muffin filled with a rich chocolate ganache!\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83c\\udf6b \\ud83d\\udd17\\u00a0FULL RECIPE LINKED IN MY BIO!\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Village Double Chocolate Muffins Ingredients \\u00a0 Makes about 9 jumbo muffins (be sure to get a jumbo pan for the best results) \\u00a0 1 Stick (8 Tablespoons) of Unsalted Butter, softened \\u00bd cup Canola or Vegetable Oil 1 Cup Sugar 1 Tablespoon Pure vanilla extract 3 Large Eggs 1 Packet (1.4 oz/39grams) instant chocolate pudding mix (Jello brand preferred) 1 \\u00bd Cups Cake Flour (Not Self-Rising) \\u00bd Cup Dark Cocoa Powder (Such as Dutch Processed) 1 Teaspoon Baking soda 1 \\u00bd Teaspoon Baking powder 3/4 tsp Fine table salt 1 cup Sour Cream 1/3 Cup Buttermilk 1 \\u00bd Cups Semi-Sweet Chocolate Chunks (I like enjoy life brand) \\u00a0 Ganache: 1 (14 oz) can of Sweetened condensed milk 1 1/4 cups Bittersweet chocolate chips (Ghiardelli is my favorite) \\u00bc teaspoon pure vanilla extract#olympics#paris2024#olympicsmuffin#chocolatemuffin#olympicvillage#olympicmuffin  The muffins at the Olympic Village are believed to be produced by\\u00a0French producer Coup de Pates.\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3862, \"end\": 3868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.868506436715162e-85, \"text\": \"Butter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butter\"}, {\"begin\": 4119, \"end\": 4124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9974102535217739, \"rank\": 0.0021970504660964213, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4337, \"end\": 4361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Condensed_milk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sweetened condensed milk\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Condensed_milk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Condensed_milk\"}, {\"begin\": 4607, \"end\": 4613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999886356104081, \"rank\": 9.898946987139715e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4614, \"end\": 4622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Record_producer\", \"score\": 0.9999901315045823, \"rank\": 9.852997708245463e-06, \"text\": \"producer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Record_producer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Record_producer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for Sodexo Live, who are handling the catering at the Olympic Village, toldPeoplethat the muffins are called 'Maxi Muffin Chocolat Intense' and they are presented in a tulip cup.\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4658, \"end\": 4664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They did not share the recipe, but they said: 'It is filled and topped with dark chocolate, featuring chunks of dark chocolate and milk chocolate.\", \"from\": 4831, \"to\": 4977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'This muffin is served daily at the main athletes' restaurant and at the six takeaway food areas within the Village.'\", \"from\": 4979, \"to\": 5096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the sweet treat is not just beloved by Henrik, as the spokesperson went on to say that a whopping 2,000 of the muffins are being consumed every day at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's thought that up to 100,000 of them will be served across the duration of the Olympics and Paralympics this year.\", \"from\": 5267, \"to\": 5384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of other Olympic athletes have also become big fans of the muffins and jumped on the TikTok trend.\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5483, \"end\": 5489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.513997469723354e-54, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with thinning or dull hair?\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts say the real issue starts at your scalp  Mother's Day gifts for new mums and mums\\u2011to\\u2011be under \\u00a350  The oral\\u2011care gadget making waves thanks to its powerful clean  Dunelm's new outdoor collection will get your garden spring-ready - from just \\u00a33  The exact blush Margot Robbie wore in Wuthering Heights and best budget alternatives  Singaporean swimmer Quah Jing Wen shared a TikTok of herself trying the chocolate treat and said it was 'fire'.\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5579, \"end\": 5584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scalp\", \"score\": 0.9987567159981766, \"rank\": 0.0012239661128435005, \"text\": \"scalp\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scalp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scalp\"}, {\"begin\": 5708, \"end\": 5714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999965016286, \"rank\": 3.498277107360068e-09, \"text\": \"Dunelm\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\"}, {\"begin\": 5806, \"end\": 5819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Margot Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\"}, {\"begin\": 5828, \"end\": 5845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wuthering_Heights\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.568908954911326e-35, \"text\": \"Wuthering Heights\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wuthering_Heights\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wuthering_Heights\"}, {\"begin\": 5876, \"end\": 5887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"score\": 0.8316461026581038, \"rank\": 0.20243173586147015, \"text\": \"Singaporean\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\"}, {\"begin\": 5888, \"end\": 5895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.834195571679532e-13, \"text\": \"swimmer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming\"}, {\"begin\": 5896, \"end\": 5909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quah_Jing_Wen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Quah Jing Wen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quah_Jing_Wen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quah_Jing_Wen\"}, {\"begin\": 5919, \"end\": 5925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.513997469723354e-54, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Bronze rugby medalist Ari Ramsey confessed that she did not like chocolate but thought the muffin was 'so moist and delicious'.\", \"from\": 5985, \"to\": 6118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a story to share?\", \"from\": 6120, \"to\": 6149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get in touch by emailingMetroLifestyleTeam@Metro.co.uk.\", \"from\": 6151, \"to\": 6206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Cadbury fans thrilled as they find twist on 'ridiculously good' discontinued chocolate  ArrowMORE:Why are some scores crossed out in diving at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 6208, \"to\": 6374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6221, \"end\": 6228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cadbury\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.616033479836332e-41, \"text\": \"Cadbury\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cadbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cadbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic champion's 'genuinely inspiring' Netflix documentary watched 8,200,000 times  Your free newsletter guide to the best London has on offer, from drinks deals to restaurant reviews.\", \"from\": 6376, \"to\": 6572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6430, \"end\": 6437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5954129237585055e-18, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": 